    <title>Zend\Form\Element</title>

    <section xml:id="zend.form.elements.intro">
        <title>Introduction</title>

        <para>
            A set of specialized elements are provided for accomplishing application-centric
            tasks. These include several HTML5 input elements with matching server-side
            validators, the <classname>Csrf</classname> element (to prevent Cross Site
            Request Forgery attacks), and the <classname>Captcha</classname> element
            (to display and validate <link linkend="zend.captcha">CAPTCHAs</link>).
        </para>

        <para>
            A <classname>Factory</classname> is provided to facilitate creation of elements,
            fieldsets, forms, and the related input filter. See the
            <link linkend="zend.form.quick-start.factory">Zend\Form Quick Start</link>
            for more information.
        </para>
    </section>

